{"word":"ἐμπηδάω","slug":"ἐμπηδάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐμπηδάω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσομαι</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐν'><el>ἐν</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to jump upon</i> a person, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to leap in</i> or <i>into</i>, <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> in aor1 <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>ἐμπηδήσας</el>, <i>eagerly, greedily</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}